6. What is Multiple Inheritance?
Multiple inheritance occurs when a class can inherit features from more than one parent class.

7. What is Polymorphism?
Polymorphism (meaning "many shapes") allows different classes to be treated as instances of the same superclass through the same interface. 


8. What is Method Resolution Order (MRO)?
MRO is the specific order in which a programming language searches for a method or attribute in a hierarchy of classes. 
